➜厦门发布双预警！“局部”暴雨侵扰！这样的雨还会持续...
http://www.sohu.com/a/417558135_100293506	42916
<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>哗啦啦～轰隆隆！</strong></span><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">今天，</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">突如其来的大暴雨</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">你有被淋到吗？</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200910/2e2abce1b532424b8ed95c65a35feb1f.gif" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">临近中午时分</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span></span><span>“局地”回波就来搅局了</span></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200910/de534eb30c594f8b9e5493e335a767fa.gif" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">湖里、同安、集美多地</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">突降暴雨， <span>电闪雷鸣！</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img height="377" width="211" src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200910/541fbf9f02b04a8d83b3b43a91bb7dfb.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
